reviewText: This DVD is far too short, only eleven songs. There is no drum solo by Carl Palmer. I saw Asia live in concert in 2010. They were great. I loved Carl's drum solo. The sound and picture quality are just average on this DVD. Not recommended.
I purchased both the CD/DVD package w. extra track on CD Coplands 'Fanfare For The Common Man'  and the DVD ( product being reviewed) and BOTH DVDs are exactly the SAME hence Redundant DVD !!!!!
